“I was under the influence of a genie” is the latest excuse for administrative
corruption in Saudi Arabia. According to the Saudi newspaper [Okaz
[Ar]](http://www.okaz.com.sa/new/Issues/20101018/Con20101018378289.htm), a
judge in Al Madina was accused of corruption, taking bribes and taking over
real estate. His defense was: “It was not me, I was under the influence of a
genie!” It is therefore no a surprise, when Saudi netizens decided to have fun
with the story. Soon enough, the hashtag #jinni -which refers to genie in
Arabic- started trending on our Twitter timelines. Here are some of the
reactions.

[Ahmad Bagadood](http://twitter.com/#!/bagadood/status/28053729623)explains
why he crossed the traffic light:

> والله يا عسكري مو أنا إللي قطعت الإشارة. هذا جني! #jinni
>
> I swear officer, it was not me who crossed the traffic light, it was a
> genie!

[Fouad Hassan ](http://twitter.com/#!/fouad_hassan/status/28028030090)calls
for the genie:

> الجني الذي دخل القاضي ماعنده حساب في تويتر نريده في حاله مستعجله ؟ #jinni من
> يعرف الطريق اليه يقول لنا بسرعه
>
> Does the genie have a Twitter account? He is needed in an urgent case!

Khalid or [@Mashi9a7](http://twitter.com/#!/Mashi9a7/status/28390351510) made
a few remarks on this:

> للإشتراك في دورة تدريببة من 5 أيام:: مهارات اختيار الجني الكفؤ، المقاعد
> محدوده #Jinni
>
> Five day workshop: “How to Pick a Genie Efficiently” subscribe now, limited
> number of seats

> #jinni مطلوب للعمل: جني لإدارة استثمارات شركة خاصة
>
> Needed: a genie to work for a private investment company

[Wajd](http://twitter.com/#!/Wajd_A/status/28010662289) announces a new movie:

> #jinni ثمرة أول تعاون جني-سعودي الفيلم السينمائي~ ليلة القبض على جني
> المدينة-تصنيف الفيلم:خيال\أطفال\كوميديا
>
> First Saudi/Genie cinema production: _“The Night the Medina Genie was
> Arrested”_ – Genre: Family / Fantasy / Comedy

As a follow up, _Okaz_ [published a story
[Ar]](http://www.okaz.com.sa/new/Issues/20101020/Con20101020378795.htm) about
a religious man named Fayez Al-Gothami who has made the genie “talk” to him in
a setting attended by some members of the religious police. According to Al-
Gothaimi, the court's judge Fahad Al-Muhaimeed, asked him to prepare a letter
explaining all the details of the interrogation and the corruption scams the
“genie” had confessed to.

[Yaser Alrefai](http://twitter.com/#!/alrefai/status/28055688372) justifies
the genie's confessions:

> عاجل: الجني المتهم يقول للراقي الذي استنطقه بأن هدفه الاساسي ليس المال بل هو
> لتسليط الضوء على أحوال الجن المحزنة بالسعودية #jinni
>
> Breaking news: the genie tells the man who talked to him that his main goal
> was not the money, but to shed the light on how the genie's community is
> treated in the kingdom

[Shaker AlSufyani](http://twitter.com/#!/S_Sufyani/status/27973775108) thinks
of taking advantage of the situation:

> أنا جالس أفكر أسوي شركة مساهمة لإستقدام الجن وذلك لخدمة البلد في السرقة
> والإساد اسميها اختصارًا فسادجنكو :P #jinni
>
> I am thinking of starting a business for hiring genies to benefit the
> country in corruption. I'll call the business “Genierruption”
>
> :P

[Essam Al-Zamel](http://twitter.com/#!/essamz/status/27978418220) remarks on
Jeddah's crises:

> اطلاق سراح جميع متهمي كارثة جدة بعد ثبوت تلبس الجن فيهم وقت توليهم للمناصب
> #Jinni
>
> The release of all people involved in Jeddah's crises, because they were
> under the spell of genies during the time they took up their positions

[wasazib](http://twitter.com/#!/wasazib/status/28005444984) would like to
improve his work situation:

> يا جماعة أبغى أزبط مديري الجديد….أحد يعرف جني فاضي من هنا و لا من هنا؟
> #jinni
>
> Guys I'd like to improve my working relation with my new manager, do you
> know any available genie?

[Feras Aalam](http://twitter.com/#!/Feras_Aalam/status/28007611037) asks to
take a serious position on this regard:

> #Jinni لابد من وقفة حازمة لمنع الجن من العبث بأمن الوطن
>
> We must take a firm stand to prevent genies from corrupting the security of
> the country

[Bader (Abu Jehad) ](http://twitter.com/#!/abujehad/status/27977270650)talks
about the release of a new book:

> قريبا في جرير حوار مع جني فاسد #Jinni
>
> Soon in bookstores: Dialog with a Corrupted Genie

[_Okaz_
[Ar]](http://www.okaz.com.sa/new/Issues/20101021/Con20101021378834.htm) then
published a story saying that the religious police denied witnessing the
“genie's hearing session.”

[MsSDigitaL](http://twitter.com/#!/MsSDigitaL/statuses/28391843824) writes:

> إذا هيئة الأمر نفت استنطاقها للجني إذا من قام بإستجواب الجني والتحقيق معه..
> شكلهم ودو الجني الأن وراء الشمس #jinni
>
> If the religious police denied hearing the genie, then who did? I believe
> the genie was made to disappear!

Finally, [Manal Fahmy](http://twitter.com/#!/manalfahmi/status/28035246337)
comments:

> Good Saudis are celebrating #halloween this year in their special way #Jinni

